This is the second version of my earlier de_remains.
The map itself mostly just changes the layout a bit and adds more detail.

Unsurprisingly, this is a bomb defusal map.

Please inform me of any bugs or glitches with either the map or the file itself.
I will most likely not make any unnecessary changes to this map beyond this version.

All feedback and or criticism is highly appreciated.
So let me know if you have any thoughts on how I could improve.
